Dis-Chem will be contributing to the government's vaccine rollout from next week, but it will cost you R70. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Dis-Chem will be contributing to the government's vaccine rollout from next week, but it will cost you R70. The company says it will be able to accommodate hundreds of people daily and will eventually operate 32 vaccination sites. READ: COVID-19 In SA: Airport screening processes intensified The fee will cover administration costs.